graph TD
    subgraph Setup
        A[User or Agent] -->|Create corpus| B[GUI or REST API]
        B -->|Apply preset or custom overrides| C[Corpus config]
        D[Embedding presets] --> B
        E[Source path or inbox folder] -->|Files available for sync| F
    end

    subgraph Ingestion
        B -->|Sync now or retry failed| F[Ingestion pipeline]
        F -->|Scan files| E
        F -->|Read effective corpus settings| C
        F --> G{Extraction lane}
        G -->|PDF| H[PyMuPDF plus OCR fallback]
        G -->|EPUB| I[EPUB extractor]
        G -->|Images| J[Tesseract or PaddleOCR]
        G -->|Code or text| K[Text loader]
        H --> L{Chunk strategy}
        I --> L
        J --> L
        K --> L
        L -->|Heading aware| M[Heading then paragraph]
        L -->|Paragraph aware| N[PDF sections]
        L -->|Code aware| O[Code symbols]
        M --> P[Chunks]
        N --> P
        O --> P
        P --> Q[Embedding provider]
        Q -->|Ollama / OpenAI / OpenRouter| R[(Qdrant per-corpus collections)]
        F -->|Track hashes, status, failures, progress| S[(SQLite state DB)]
    end

    subgraph Retrieval
        T[User or Agent query] --> U[Query engine]
        U -->|List corpora when needed| V[Corpus API]
        U -->|Load corpus config| C
        U -->|Embed query with corpus embedding model| Q
        U -->|Search top-k| R
        R -->|Hits| W[Optional reranker]
        W --> X[Answer provider]
        X -->|Ollama / OpenAI / Anthropic / OpenRouter| Y[Answer plus citations]
    end
